Follow instructions on installing Julia nd ACEpotentials.jl v0.6.10:

https://acesuit.github.io/ACEpotentials.jl/v0.6/gettingstarted/installation/

You would also need to have JuLIP installed for structural relaxation:
https://github.com/JuliaMolSim/JuLIP.jl

Use the attached Project.toml file to download the required Julia dependencies and follow these instructions:

The first time you activate this project, in the REPL, you can switch to Pkg mode by typing ], and type the command instantiate. This will cause the package manager to download and install all of the packages listed in Project.toml and their dependencies.

Read more from here: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/72061475/installing-julia-packages-using-a-toml-file

